Code and input for evaluating performance of tree communication classes.

We test various combinations of tree arangements, message size and
communication patterns.  See the individual input files for details.

COMPILATION AND EXECUTION
-------------------------

   Compilation:
      make main

   Execution:
      For one the following input files in test_inputs:
      serial:
         ./main <input file>
      parallel:
         Parallel execution is platform dependent.  This example demonstrates
         execution via mpirun.
         mpirun -np <nprocs> [mpirun options] ./main <input file>
